%% Data Flow Diagram - OpenVINO Model Server (OVMS)
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Platform as KServe/ModelMesh<br/>(Platform Gateway)
    participant REST as OVMS REST Server<br/>rest_port/TCP HTTP
    participant gRPC as OVMS gRPC Server<br/>grpc_port/TCP gRPC
    participant KFS as KServe v2 Handler
    participant OpenAIH as OpenAI v3 Handler
    participant SM as Servable Manager
    participant MP as MediaPipe Graph<br/>Executor
    participant OV as OpenVINO Runtime
    participant S3 as Remote Storage<br/>S3/GCS/Azure/HF<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: REST KServe v2 Inference
    Client->>Platform: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer
    Platform->>REST: Forward request<br/>(mTLS via Service Mesh)
    REST->>KFS: Route to KFS handler
    KFS->>SM: Get model instance
    SM->>OV: Execute inference
    OV-->>SM: Inference result
    SM-->>KFS: Response
    KFS-->>REST: JSON response
    REST-->>Platform: HTTP 200
    Platform-->>Client: Inference result

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: gRPC KServe v2 Inference
    Client->>Platform: gRPC ModelInfer
    Platform->>gRPC: Forward (gRPC/HTTP2)
    gRPC->>KFS: Route to KFS service
    KFS->>SM: Get model instance
    SM->>OV: Execute inference
    OV-->>SM: Result tensors
    SM-->>KFS: Response
    KFS-->>gRPC: gRPC response
    gRPC-->>Platform: InferResponse
    Platform-->>Client: Inference result

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: OpenAI-Compatible LLM Chat/Completions (v3)
    Client->>Platform: POST /v3/chat/completions
    Platform->>REST: Forward request
    REST->>OpenAIH: Route to v3 handler
    OpenAIH->>MP: Execute MediaPipe graph
    MP->>OV: LLM inference<br/>(continuous batching)
    OV-->>MP: Token generation
    MP-->>OpenAIH: Stream/complete response
    OpenAIH-->>REST: SSE stream or JSON
    REST-->>Platform: Response
    Platform-->>Client: Chat completion

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: Model Loading from Remote Storage
    SM->>S3: HTTPS GET model artifacts<br/>TLS 1.2+, IAM/credentials
    S3-->>SM: Model files
    SM->>OV: Load & optimize model
    OV-->>SM: Model ready
